633
00:42:05,825 --> 00:42:08,427
Dapat bago ka dito.

634
00:42:08,427 --> 00:42:09,795
Kasama ko ang Bagong Negosyo...

635
00:42:10,563 --> 00:42:13,199
Ibig sabihin, ako si Manager Seong Tae Hun
